rating_comment: Very accommodating host. They are responsive and helpful. The place is clean and they have housekeepers who will help you with your needs during your stay. The internet is very fast, unexpectedly so. Tons restaurants near the place which makes it very convenient. I absolutely recommend this place especially for the price it’s being offered rn
